      "content": "i get the balance thing, but it feels like the arguments for the hikes are always about \"fairness\" and \"dignity,\" while the actual math for business owners is ignored. if i have to raise my prices just to keep up with a wage hike that doesn't even match the local economy, aren't the people pushing for this basically ignoring the reality of how small towns work?",
